reviewText: One of the ladies gets topless multiple times. A second one gets topless 2-3 times and the third gives two very quick flashes.
This was the WORST movie I have even seen. I was stunned at how horrible it was. I like a good "B" movie now and then but this is SO much WORSE it was beyond belief that it was even released.

Even as a diehard Corman New World fan, I didn't expect much from "Cover Girl Models", yet I was pleased to find it an exciting little action film. The girls are beautiful, likeable, funny and intelligent, ultimately proving their resourcefulness when caught up in international intrigue. Entertaining from beginning to end. It deserves to be reproduced on DVD with a better print and special features.
